Subject: [PATCH 64/64] web-app: show live download percentage on the
 'downloading' message bubble

Core now emits DownloadProgress (msgId, permille) while fetching a message
in chunks. useDownloadProgress listens for it per-message and appends the
percent to the existing label; the published jsonrpc-client pin predates
the event so its type is widened locally (same pattern already used for
DefaultCredentials.ts's `webimap` field).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
